{"id": "art-272", "label": "Art. 272", "title": "Art. 272", "slug": "art-272", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1763277104\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1091\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1763277104\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 272 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1032672761\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1090\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1032672761\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Se <span\nclass=SpellE>pedepse&#351;te</span> cu închisoare de la 6 luni la 3 ani ori cu\namend&#259; fondatorul, administratorul, directorul general, directorul,\nmembrul consiliului de supraveghere sau al directoratului ori reprezentantul\nlegal al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_893735954\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1089\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_893735954\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<span class=SpellE>dobânde&#351;te</span>, în contul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nale altor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>, la un <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;</span> pe care îl <span class=SpellE>&#351;tie</span>\nv&#259;dit superior valorii lor efective, sau vinde, pe seama <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\npe care aceasta le <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span>, la <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;uri</span> despre care are <span class=SpellE>cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;</span>\nc&#259; sunt v&#259;dit inferioare valorii lor efective, în scopul <span\nclass=SpellE>ob&#355;inerii</span>, pentru el sau pentru alte persoane, a unui\nfolos în paguba <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_239622690\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1088\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_239622690\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>folose&#351;te</span>, cu rea-<span\nclass=SpellE>credin&#355;&#259;</span>, bunuri sau creditul de care se\nbucur&#259; societatea, într-un scop contrar intereselor acesteia sau în\nfolosul lui propriu ori pentru a favoriza o alt&#259; societate în care are\ninterese direct sau indirect;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_470498746\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1087\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_470498746\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)se împrumut&#259;, sub orice form&#259;, direct sau\nprintr-o persoan&#259; interpus&#259;, de la societatea pe care o\nadministreaz&#259;, de la o societate controlat&#259; de aceasta ori de la o\nsocietate care controleaz&#259; societatea pe care el o administreaz&#259;,\nsuma împrumutat&#259; fiind superioar&#259; limitei prev&#259;zute la art. 144<sup>4</sup>\nalin. (3) lit. a), sau face ca una dintre aceste <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\ns&#259; îi acorde vreo <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ie</span> pentru datorii\nproprii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1144455047\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1086\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1144455047\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)încalc&#259; <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. 183.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_100556839\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1085\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_100556839\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Nu constituie <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iune</span>\nfapta prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) lit. b), dac&#259; a fost <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;it&#259;</span> de administratorul, directorul,\nmembrul directoratului ori reprezentantul legal al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nîn cadrul unor <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> de trezorerie între\nsocietate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> alte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\ncontrolate de aceasta sau care o controleaz&#259;, direct ori indirect.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_176808418\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1084\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_176808418\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Nu constituie <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iune</span>\nfapta prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) lit. c), dac&#259; este <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;it&#259;</span> de c&#259;tre o societate ce are\ncalitatea de fondator, iar împrumutul este realizat de la una dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> controlate ori care o\ncontroleaz&#259; pe aceasta, direct sau indirect.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}